<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Grow With Carbon Cube Kenya</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css');
    
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
    }
    .email-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1f2937 0%, #374151 100%);
      color: #fff;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px 20px;
    }
    .logo img {
      height: 55px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .header p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #d1d5db;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px 25px;
    }
    .greeting {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #111827;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .intro {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #374151;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }
    .seller-info {
      background: #f9fafb;
      padding: 18px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
    .seller-info h3 {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #111827;
    }
    .seller-info div {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #374151;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .shop-link {
      background: #eef2ff;
      border: 1px dashed #6366f1;
      padding: 14px;
      margin: 15px 0 30px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #1e3a8a;
      word-break: break-all;
    }
    .shop-link strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      color: #111827;
    }
    .message {
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      color: #374151;
    }
    .message h4 {
      font-size: 16px;
      margin: 20px 0 8px;
      color: #111827;
    }
    .message ul {
      margin: 0 0 15px 18px;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .message li {
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .cta {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }
    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 6px;
      padding: 12px 28px;
      border-radius: 25px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #fff !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 15px;
      transition: transform .2s ease;
    }
    .cta-button.blue {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F7B500 0%, #e6a200 100%);
    }
    .cta-button.green {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1f2937 0%, #374151 100%);
    }
    .cta-button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #6b7280;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
    .footer p {
      margin: 6px 0;
    }
    .social-links a {
      color: #F7B500;
      margin: 0 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    
    /* Icon styles */
    .icon {
      color: #F7B500;
      margin-right: 8px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .icon-large {
      color: #F7B500;
      margin-right: 10px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    
    <!-- HEADER -->
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">
        <img src="https://carboncube-ke.com/logo.png" alt="Carbon Cube Kenya" />
      </div>
      <p>Kenya's Most Trusted Online Marketplace</p>
    </div>

    <!-- CONTENT -->
    <div class="content">

      <!-- Greeting -->
      <div class="greeting">Dear <%= @seller.fullname %>,</div>
      <div class="intro">
        We’re excited to share that <strong>Carbon Cube Kenya is growing rapidly</strong>, with more buyers joining the marketplace every single day.  
        <br><br>
        This growth means <strong>increased visibility for your products, stronger demand across categories, and more chances to connect with customers</strong> who are actively searching for what you offer.  
        <br><br>
        As the platform expands, top-performing sellers are already seeing <strong>higher engagement, more inquiries, and faster sales cycles</strong>. By staying active and keeping your shop updated, you position yourself to capture this momentum and stand out in a competitive market.  
        <br><br>
        Now is the perfect time to <strong>optimize your shop, upload fresh ads, and engage with buyers</strong> — every small action you take today compounds as Carbon Cube Kenya continues to grow.
      </div>

      <!-- Seller Performance -->
      <div class="seller-info">
        <h3><i class="fas fa-chart-bar icon-large"></i>Your Shop Performance</h3>
        <div>
          <strong>Shop:</strong> <%= @seller.enterprise_name %><br>
          <strong>Location:</strong> <%= @seller.location %><br>
          <strong>Email:</strong> <%= @seller.email %><br>
          <strong>Total Ads:</strong> <%= @seller.ads.count %><br>
          <strong>Reviews:</strong> <%= @seller.reviews.count %> (Avg: <%= @seller.reviews.average(:rating)&.round(1) || "N/A" %>)<br>
          <strong>Tier:</strong> <%= @seller.seller_tier&.tier_id || "Free" %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Shop Link -->
      <div class="shop-link">
        <strong><i class="fas fa-link icon"></i>Your Shop Link:</strong>
        https://carboncube-ke.com/shop/<%= @seller.enterprise_name&.downcase&.gsub(/\s+/, '-')&.gsub(/[^a-z0-9\-]/, '') %>
        <br><br>
        Copy and share this link on <strong>WhatsApp, Facebook, Instagram, and with your customers</strong> to bring more buyers directly to your shop!
      </div>

      <!-- Action Steps -->
      <div class="message">
        To help you maximize your success, here are a few proven steps:
        
        <h4><i class="fas fa-check-circle icon"></i>Complete Your Shop Profile</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Add a professional profile picture</li>
          <li>Update your business description</li>
          <li>Verify your contact details</li>
        </ul>

        <h4><i class="fas fa-shopping-cart icon"></i>Upload Ads Actively</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>List new products regularly</li>
          <li>Use high-quality photos</li>
          <li>Write detailed descriptions</li>
        </ul>

        <h4><i class="fas fa-bullhorn icon"></i>Promote Your Shop</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Share your shop link on social media</li>
          <li>Add it to your email signature</li>
          <li>Encourage friends and family to visit</li>
        </ul>

        <h4><i class="fas fa-handshake icon"></i>Stay Engaged</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Respond quickly to inquiries</li>
          <li>Refresh your listings often</li>
          <li>Check your dashboard for insights</li>
        </ul>

        Together, we’re building something amazing. <strong>Your growth is our priority!</strong>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA Buttons -->
      <div class="cta">
        <a href="https://carboncube-ke.com/seller/dashboard" class="cta-button blue">Visit Dashboard</a>
        <a href="https://carboncube-ke.com/shop/<%= @seller.enterprise_name&.downcase&.gsub(/\s+/, '-')&.gsub(/[^a-z0-9\-]/, '') %>" class="cta-button green">View My Shop</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FOOTER -->
    <div class="footer">
      <!-- Footer Logo -->
      <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <img src="https://carboncube-ke.com/logo.png" alt="Carbon Cube Kenya" style="height: 40px; margin-bottom: 8px;" />
        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280;">Kenya's Most Trusted Online Marketplace</p>
      </div>
      
      <p>Best regards,<br><strong>The Carbon Cube Kenya Team</strong></p>
      
      <!-- Contact Information -->
      <div style="margin: 15px 0; padding: 15px; background: #fef7e0; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #F7B500;">
        <h4 style="margin: 0 0 10px; font-size: 14px; color: #111827;"><i class="fas fa-phone icon"></i>Need Help? Contact Us:</h4>
        <div style="font-size: 13px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">
          <strong><i class="fas fa-envelope icon"></i>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:info@carboncube-ke.com" style="color: #F7B500; text-decoration: none;">info@carboncube-ke.com</a><br>
          <strong><i class="fas fa-mobile-alt icon"></i>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:+254712990524" style="color: #F7B500; text-decoration: none;">+254 712 990 524</a><br>
          <strong><i class="fab fa-whatsapp icon"></i>WhatsApp:</strong> <a href="https://wa.me/254712990524" style="color: #F7B500; text-decoration: none;">+254 712 990 524</a><br>
          <strong><i class="fas fa-clock icon"></i>Hours:</strong> Monday - Friday, 8:00 AM - 5:00 PM EAT<br>
          <strong><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt icon"></i>Location:</strong> 9th Floor, CMS Africa, Kilimani, Nairobi, Kenya
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="social-links">
        <a href="https://carboncube-ke.com" style="color: #F7B500;">Website</a> | 
        <a href="https://carboncube-ke.com/support" style="color: #F7B500;">Support</a> | 
        <a href="https://carboncube-ke.com/help" style="color: #F7B500;">Help Center</a>
      </div>
      <p>© 2025 Carbon Cube Kenya. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
